HEADWORD: Elapidae
<hw>Elapidae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a natural family of snakes
including the cobras, kraits, mambas, the New World coral snakes, and
Australian taipan and tiger snakes.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Elapidae</fam>.</syn>⟦br⟧
